{"tid":928267,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭生斷言癌症不再是絕症！？回應頭條一二事！〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉2018-12-04","createTime":"2018-12-04T17:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T06:55:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fda94ccfcdf4903f6c06fd06db306072de9223a","tid":928267,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"蕭生斷言癌症不再是絕症！？回應頭條一二事！〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉2018-12-04<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X1_EFiDyNBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX1_EFiDyNBI&d=qmBz6ZN77ZI7cUQ0dYhunsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=b388b333\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X1_EFiDyNBI</a>"},{"pid":"9420fcb4b5dffe8b0a03bb6140ef115aa57b618c","tid":928267,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"【最新蕭析】蕭若元：唔鍾意蕭定一同內地人做生意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543934467_32a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543934467_32a8.jpg&h=2d83664c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蕭若元在網台上提到，大約三個月前知道兒子蕭定一生意上「出咗事」。<br />\n<br />\nHMV數碼中國（8078）主席蕭定一，名下位於中環及銅鑼灣的唱片店HMV，被指拖欠租金，遭追討近500萬元欠租及賠償。有報道指蕭定一正尋求投資者入股打救，惟成事機會不大，HMV或面臨全線結業。公司晚上發公告指，可能進行未來計劃，但不限於重組、投資、清盤和出售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕭定一父親、時事評論員蕭若元在網台上提到，大約三個月前知道兒子「出咗事」，因此心情比較低落。他指大家「無理大家嘅生意10幾年」，事關蕭定一的生意營運手法，違反了其原則，就是不和內地人做生意。而蕭定一則經常與內地人做生意，他覺得兒子今次出事，有經濟因素、亦有消費因素等影響。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181204/58992991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58992991&d=qmBz6ZN77ZI7cUQ0dYhunsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=6a8b4025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58992991&h=683f129b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181204/58992991</a>"},{"pid":"30dd3d173907d7b805fc8ce58418b372a68b3639","tid":928267,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"蕭定一撲水 兩年4按西半山豪宅<br />\n【明報專訊】蕭定一旗下音樂連鎖店HMV被供應商及業主連環入稟「追數」，另一邊廂據土地註冊處資料顯示，蕭定一兩年前以約1.5億元購入的西半山豪宅殷然頂層天池屋，今年10月再度被用作抵押貸款，過去兩年合共先後四度承按，成為蕭定一的私人「提款機」。<br />\n<br />\n三按後曾清還借貸 今年10月再抵押<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，蕭定一在2016年6月以約1.5億元，向太古地產（1972）購入的西半山殷然頂層天池屋，過去兩年已四度用作抵押借貸，首次是在2017年5月由匯豐銀行承做一按。至去年10月，由一名張姓人士以私人名義借出二按，今年7月再由Great Panorama International Limited承做三按，其後雖然一度清還借貸，至今年10月再抵押予浩瀚資產管理有限公司貸款。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20181204/s00004/1543861298115/%E8%95%AD%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%92%B2%E6%B0%B4-%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B44%E6%8C%89%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20181204%2Fs00004%2F1543861298115%2F%25E8%2595%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2592%25B2%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B44%25E6%258C%2589%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585&d=qmBz6ZN77ZI7cUQ0dYhunsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=065e7afb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20181204%2Fs00004%2F1543861298115%2F%25E8%2595%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2592%25B2%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B44%25E6%258C%2589%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585&h=6b37647b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20181204/s00004/1543861298115/%E8%95%AD%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%92%B2%E6%B0%B4-%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B44%E6%8C%89%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85</a>"},{"pid":"1f5eaecd6842f928a201baacb992e07e1b80b86a","tid":928267,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"仆街了<br />\n癌症以後都唔洗醫<br />\n會變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}